snippet.description:
Meri Bassai is one of the longest and most popular Nepali comedy serials with 18 Years of broadcasting. Based on rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people, the series represents many political and social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavor. It is aired in Nepal Television at 8:50 PM and in YouTube at 9:30 PM every Tuesday. This show is produced by Media Hub Pvt. Ltd. 

The story is based on the rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people. The show represents many political as well as social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavour.

snippet.title: Đừng nghĩ bự con là ngon nha | Ben Eagle | #Shorts
snippet.description:
#beneagle #vothuat #tuve
Cảm ơn các bạn đã xem và đăng ký ủng hộ kênh của Ben nha!!!

Ben là người sáng lập ra Eagles Training Center - Trung tâm huấn luyện võ thuật điện ảnh và tự vệ thực chiến, hiện trung tâm đã hoạt động được hơn 10 năm tại Việt Nam, tham gia rất nhiều bộ phim hành động võ thuật và đào tạo ra rất nhiều cascadeur và diễn viên võ thuật cho điện ảnh Việt Nam. Với hơn 20 năm kinh nghiệm về võ thuật tổng hợp, rèn luyện đa dạng các bộ môn võ thuật khác nhau, Ben có góc nhìn khá tổng quát và trung lập về võ thuật hiện đại, sử dụng các đòn thế đẹp mắt để áp dụng vào các bộ phim hành động võ thuật, đồng thời không quên tính thực chiến và hiệu quả của nhiều đòn thế tự vệ để thực thi khi hữu dụng. 
Tại Eagles Training Center các bạn được đào tạo chính về: tự vệ thực chiến, võ điện ảnh, võ hiện đại, cascadeur/stuntman,  parkour, sasuke, fitness. Eagles Training Center sẽ giúp những bạn có ước mơ trở thành diễn viên hành động/ngôi sao võ thuật tiếp cận với nghiệp diễn, song song với phát triển kỹ năng tự vệ tổng hợp, đồng thời xây dựng hình thể và kiểm soát cân nặng của mình, giúp các bạn vừa rèn luyện sức khỏe vừa có vóc dáng đẹp.

Clip thuộc bản quyền của Ben Eagle, vui lòng không reup, cảm ơn!!!
Do not reup, thanks!!!

snippet.title: Super Lover | 2023 New Release Telugu Hindi Dub Full Movie | Naga Shaurya, Rashi Khanna, South Movie
snippet.description:
Movie Name   Super Lover ( Dubbed From Oohalu Gusagusalade )
Producer : Surinder Yadav ( Hindi )  Sai Korapati ( Telugu ) 
Directed  :  Srinivas Avasarala 
Movie Starring #NagaShourya, #rashikhanna  & Srinivas Avasarala. 
composed by Kalyani Koduri.

N Venkateshwara Rao (Naga Shourya) is an youngster whose ambition is to become a famous TV newsreader just like his bedridden father. He works in a TV studio that is owned by Uday (Srinivas Avasarala). Uday is a socially awkward guy and is bad at communicating with women. Venkateswara Rao falls in love with Prabhavathi (Rashi Khanna) few years back when he visits a relative in Vizag. They break-up because of a misunderstanding. The rest of the story is all about what happens when Uday wants to impress upon Prabhavathi.

snippet.title: बसंत पंचमी स्पेशल भजन 2023 | Vasant Panchami Special Aarti | Saraswati Pooja | Om Jai Saraswati Mata
snippet.description:
बसंत पंचमी स्पेशल भजन 2023 | Vasant Panchami Special Bhajan | Saraswati Pooja | Basant Panchami Bhajan | Om Jai Saraswati Mata Aarti | Saraswati Chalisa | Saraswati Vandana | Jai Devi Saraswati.

00:00 - 01 Om Jai Saraswati Mata by Pamela Jain
08:08 - 02 Jai Saraswati Mata by Shweta Thakur and Aditya Jayant Ankam
13:40 - 03 Saraswati Chalisa by Minakshi Mazumdar
24:45 - 04 Saraswati Vandana by Devyani Kothari

Title - Om Jai Saraswati Mata
Singer - Pamela Jain
Lyricist: Traditional
Album - Devotional Bhakti Songs Vol. 3
MUSIC COMPOSERS - Avijit Das

Title - Jai Saraswati Mata
Singer - Shweta Thakur and Aditya Jayant Ankam
Lyricist: Traditional
Album - Soulful Mantras Bhajans Vol 3
MUSIC COMPOSERS - Sourabh Kumar

Title - Saraswati Chalisa
Singer - Minakshi Mazumdar
Lyricist: Traditional
Album - Devotional Bhakti Songs Vol. 1
MUSIC COMPOSERS - Goutam Banerjee

Title - Saraswati Vandana ( Jai Devi Saraswati )
Singer - Devyani Kothari
Lyricist: Traditional
Album - Devotional Bhajans
MUSIC COMPOSERS - Studio Sound Garage

On our "Spiritual Mantra" channel you will find your beloved deities favorite Bhajan, Mantras, Aarti, Jaap, Chant, Shloka, Amritwani, Kirtan, Pravchan and LIVE darshan etc. 

You can enjoy variour popular bhajan like Shree Krishna Bhajan, Hanuman ji Bhajan, Ganesh ji Bhajan, Shri Ram Bhajan, Shri Laxmi Mata ke Bhajan, Santoshi Maa ke Bhajan, Sherawali Mata ke Bhajan, Shiv Shankar Bhajan, Vishnu Bhajan, Balaji Bhajan, Saibaba Bhajan, Devi Maa ke Bhajan etc. 

Listen to very popular and famous aartiyan like; Aarti Kunj Bihari Ki, Aarti Shri Ramayan Ji Ki, Aarti Kije Hanuman Lala Ki, Sri Gayatri Mata ki Aarti, Om Jai Lakshmi Mata, Om Jai Jagdish Hare, Aarti Sai Baba, Jai Ganesh Deva, Jai Lakshmi Mata, Om Jai Ambe Gauri, Om Jai Shiv Omkara, Aarti Hanuman Ji Ki, Jai Santoshi Mata, Om Jai Shri Shani Deva, Jai Ganesh Deva, Om Jai Shiv Omkara, Ambe Tu Hai Jagdambe etc. 

Also you can enjoy chalisa of your beloved deities like Hanuman Chalisa, Brahma Chalisa, Saraswati Chalisa, Vaishno Devi Chalisa, Krishna Chalisa, Ganesh Chalisa, Durga Chalisa,  Sarasvati Chalisa, Laxmi Chalisa, Shree Ram Chalisa,  Shiv Chalisa, Durga Chalisa, Santoshi Maa Chalisa etc.

Find very popular mantras like Mahamrityunjay Mantra, Gayatri Mantra, Ganesh Mantra, Morning Mantra, Laxmi Mantra, Shiv Mantra, Shani Mantra, Vishnu Sahasranamam Mantra, Shree Siddhivinayak Mantra, Hanuman Mantra, bhajan like Yashomati Maiya Se Bole Nandlala sung by Lata Mangeshkar and other very known singers like Anuradha Paudwal, Kavita Paudwal, Suresh Wadkar, Anup Jalota, Sadhana Sargam, Bela Shende, Shankar Mahadevan, Narendra Chanchal, Richa Sharma, Asha Bhosle, Usha Mangeshkar etc.

en-IN.description:
बसंत पंचमी स्पेशल भजन 2023 | Vasant Panchami Special Bhajan | Saraswati Pooja | Basant Panchami Bhajan | Om Jai Saraswati Mata Aarti | Saraswati Chalisa | Saraswati Vandana | Jai Devi Saraswati.

08:08 - 02 Jai Saraswati Mata by Shweta Thakur and Aditya Jayant Ankam

Lyricist: Traditional

Singer - Devyani Kothari
Lyricist: Traditional
Album - Devotional Bhajans
MUSIC COMPOSERS - Studio Sound Garage

On our "Spiritual Mantra" channel you will find your beloved deities favorite Bhajan, Mantras, Aarti, Jaap, Chant, Shloka, Amritwani, Kirtan, Pravchan and LIVE darshan etc. 

You can enjoy variour popular bhajan like Shree Krishna Bhajan, Hanuman ji Bhajan, Ganesh ji Bhajan, Shri Ram Bhajan, Shri Laxmi Mata ke Bhajan, Santoshi Maa ke Bhajan, Sherawali Mata ke Bhajan, Shiv Shankar Bhajan, Vishnu Bhajan, Balaji Bhajan, Saibaba Bhajan, Devi Maa ke Bhajan etc. 

Listen to very popular and famous aartiyan like; Aarti Kunj Bihari Ki, Aarti Shri Ramayan Ji Ki, Aarti Kije Hanuman Lala Ki, Sri Gayatri Mata ki Aarti, Om Jai Lakshmi Mata, Om Jai Jagdish Hare, Aarti Sai Baba, Jai Ganesh Deva, Jai Lakshmi Mata, Om Jai Ambe Gauri, Om Jai Shiv Omkara, Aarti Hanuman Ji Ki, Jai Santoshi Mata, Om Jai Shri Shani Deva, Jai Ganesh Deva, Om Jai Shiv Omkara, Ambe Tu Hai Jagdambe etc. 

Also you can enjoy chalisa of your beloved deities like Hanuman Chalisa, Brahma Chalisa, Saraswati Chalisa, Vaishno Devi Chalisa, Krishna Chalisa, Ganesh Chalisa, Durga Chalisa,  Sarasvati Chalisa, Laxmi Chalisa, Shree Ram Chalisa,  Shiv Chalisa, Durga Chalisa, Santoshi Maa Chalisa etc.

Find very popular mantras like Mahamrityunjay Mantra, Gayatri Mantra, Ganesh Mantra, Morning Mantra, Laxmi Mantra, Shiv Mantra, Shani Mantra, Vishnu Sahasranamam Mantra, Shree Siddhivinayak Mantra, Hanuman Mantra, bhajan like Yashomati Maiya Se Bole Nandlala sung by Lata Mangeshkar and other very known singers like Anuradha Paudwal, Kavita Paudwal, Suresh Wadkar, Anup Jalota, Sadhana Sargam, Bela Shende, Shankar Mahadevan, Narendra Chanchal, Richa Sharma, Asha Bhosle, Usha Mangeshkar etc.

मान्छे बाँचुन्जेल पो मान्छे हुन्छ त । मरे पछि त उ मरेको मान्छे हुन्छ । प्राण वायुले शरिरका पुर्जा चलुन्जेल पो मान्छे ! 
मरेपछि मान्छेभित्रको प्राण कहाँ जान्छ ? मेची किनारका विश्वनाथ हरिजनलाई यस्ता कुरा सोच्ने फुर्सद छैन । उनलाई यत्ति थाहा छ, मरेपछि मान्छे मुर्दाघरमा जान्छ र उनलाई जिउँदै पनि मुर्दाघर जानुपर्छ । 
#hernekatha 

A person is a person as long as they are alive. After death, one becomes a dead body. 
“Where does one’s soul go after death?” Vishwanath Harijan does not have time for these questions. All he knows is that a person is taken to the morgue after death. However, he himself goes to the morgue alive.

snippet.title: Women Power | South Superhit Movies | Jyothika, Nayanthara, Keerthy Suresh, Samantha
snippet.description:
Movie:- Madam Geeta Rani (Raatchasi)
Starcast:- Jyothika, Hareesh Peradi, Poornima Bhagyaraj, Sathyan, Nagineedu, Aruldoss

The film is about a headmaster converting a poorly run school into one of the best in the state.

Movie:- Tejasvini (Aramm)
Starcast:- Nayanthara, Sunu Lakshmi, Ramachandran Durairaj, Kitty, Vela Ramamoorthy

A little girl falls into a deep borewell, and her rescue becomes a huge professional and personal challenge for a collector.

Movie:- Mahanati
Starcast:- Keerthy Suresh, Dulquer Salmaan, Samantha, Vijay Deverakonda, Naga Chaitanya, Rajendra Prasad, Bhanupriya, Malavika Nair 

Savitri, the most admired actress from South Indian cinema, goes through various tragic incidents in her personal life. Unable to cope with depression, she eventually becomes an alcoholic.

Movie:- U Turn
Starcast:- Samantha Akkineni, Aadhi Pinisetty, Rahul Ravindran, Bhumika Chawla, Ravi Prakash, Ashish Vidyarthi

The plot revolves around the death of motorists who break a traffic rule at a particular flyover in Hyderabad and the subsequent pinning down of the culprit by an intern journalist and police inspector duo.

snippet.description:

snippet.title: 😍OMG! World's Largest River Cruise GangaVilas #shorts
snippet.description:
#shorts
For "HUGE" Discount on 3D Animation Course, Call: +91-99830-83303 or Click here 👉🏻 https://professorofhow.com

😍OMG! World's Largest River Cruise GangaVilas #shorts 

Finally, PM Narendra Modi inaugurated the world's longest river cruise. But the price of a single trip on this cruise will definitely boggle your brain. This Ganga Vilas named cruise will cover a 3200KM of distance in 50 Days.
This cruise will board from Varanasi, it will reach Bangladesh via Farakka, and will enter India once again completing its first course at Dibrugarh.
This trip will include cultural events like Ganga Aarti, UNESCO heritage sites like Sunderban and Kaziranga National Park, and a lot of other amazing things.
This cruise consists of 18 luxurious suites, where you'll get convertible beds, a French balcony, LED TVs, etc. Apart from this, this ship includes a restaurant, bar, open observation deck for enjoying the sunset, gym, and spa as well. Cultural programs will also be organized for your entertainment.
If we talk about the price of a single ticket, so there is no official disclosure available. But as the tickets for this cruise have got sold out for the next 1.5 years, at the rate of 46.7K USD per suite, it simply indicates that this cruise cannot be afforded by a major portion of Indian citizens. According to the operators, the per day cost for this cruise is said to be around 300 USD only.

snippet.title: How do Fish Breath Underwater? #shorts
snippet.description:
#shorts
For "HUGE" Discount on 3D Animation Course, Call: +91-99830-83303 or Click here 👉🏻 https://professorofhow.com

How do Fish Breath Underwater? #shorts 

If someone drowned your head in water, nothing will be more important for you than taking your head out for breathing. But how does a fish spends its whole life inside water? Double tap the screen and let's understand the science behind fish breathing inside water.
A fish consists of two gills on both sides of its head behind its eyes, these gills remain covered by the operculum. The breathing process in fish takes place in 2 steps.
First - The opercula and the mouth of fish both combined work as a pump, which makes water move inside the mouth of the fish through gills and takes it out of the water, this pumping is called buccal pumping.
Second - When water moves through gills, because of the numerous capillaries present in the gills, they work as a filter. These filters absorb oxygen from the water and drain the water and CO2 out of the body.
The absorbed oxygens get bonded with hemoglobin and reach the entire body and completed the breathing process.
However, the fishes like whales and dolphins cannot breathe underwater, they can remain inside the water for a long time without breathing and approach the surface of the water to inhale oxygen.
